knock you in to next week.

24:26.398 --> 24:28.532
- He wasn't a bad person.

24:30.602 --> 24:31.869
He was broken.

24:31.871 --> 24:32.871
- Broken?

24:35.440 --> 24:39.643
- I know you don't get
it, you don't understand.

24:39.645 --> 24:43.247
- No I do get it,
i do understand.

24:43.249 --> 24:45.649
You've been brainwashed.

24:45.651 --> 24:47.017
- You're not listening to me,

24:47.019 --> 24:49.720
this isn't something that
he forced me to feel.

24:49.722 --> 24:50.722
