that he broke you.

25:04.170 --> 25:05.236
- No.

25:05.238 --> 25:06.070
- No?

25:06.072 --> 25:08.038
- No he even took off the ties.

25:08.040 --> 25:11.942
- Let me ask you this,
were you free to leave?

25:13.645 --> 25:17.882
