- Good morning.

25:50.815 --> 25:51.815
Here.

25:56.288 --> 25:58.956
- No, can I eat something else?

26:02.027 --> 26:03.027
- Like?

26:04.563 --> 26:06.697
- Have you got any fruit?

26:54.479 --> 26:56.981
