I'll stop.

29:31.302 --> 29:32.536
I'll be quiet.

29:35.840 --> 29:36.840
I promise.

30:01.132 --> 30:04.034
- You have
a very beautiful voice.

30:05.637 --> 30:06.703
- Thank you.

30:10.141 --> 30:11.809
- Are you a singer?

30:17.482 --> 30:18.482
- I was.

30:23.054 --> 30:24.888
I did a lot of shows.

30:26.391 --> 30:28.692
I sang for a lot of people.

30:37.836 --> 30:41.205
