about someone.

40:43.341 --> 40:46.075
- Oh I'm not looking for anyone.

40:47.745 --> 40:49.846
- Life, life isn't worth living

40:49.848 --> 40:53.316
unless you have someone
to share it with.

40:55.252 --> 40:56.085
