45:19.551 --> 45:20.850
- He let me go.

45:22.319 --> 45:25.054
- He let you go, just like that.

45:26.824 --> 45:31.027
- I think he finally realized
that he couldn't keep me.

45:33.864 --> 45:36.799
- And how did he come
to that conclusion?

45:36.801 --> 45:41.003
- Well we started becoming
friends and getting closer.

